'''''Internetowa encyklopedia PWN''''' ([[Polish language|Polish]] for ''Internet PWN Encyclopedia'') is a free online Polish-language [[encyclopedia]] published by [[Wydawnictwo Naukowe PWN]]. It contains some 80,000 entries and 5,000 illustrations.

